-- South African Retail Sales Rose 6.4% in June, Industry Association Says
-- Mike Cohen
-- 2010-07-23T10:12:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/south-african-retail-sales-rose-6-4-in-june-industry-association-says.html

          
          
             South African retail sales rose 6.4
percent in June from a year ago, the Retailer Liaison Committee,
an industry body, said in an e-mailed statement today.  
